Package jopt.js.spi.domain.listener

Interface Summary
ActivityDomainListener Interface that can be implemented by a class that wishes to be notified of changes to the activity domain
OperationDomainListener Interface that can be implemented by a class that wishes to be notified of changes to the operations of an activity domain
